Comic relief provides humor to the serie: Tragic hero experiences a downfall due to their flaws
Redeemed villain is a character who switches from villain to hero
Villainess is a female antagonist with evil intentions
Schemer is a character that plots or manipulates others
Hero is a protagonist with noble qualities
Mentor is a wise guide to the protagonist
Antihero is a protagonist with morally ambiguous qualities
Shapeshifter changes their form or identity
Sidekick is a supportive character to the hero
